OL,7,FOur investigation has found:
OL,9,FWhat is 'chemsex'?
OL,11,FIt's a term you've possibly never
OL,12,Fheard of - 'chemsex' or chemical sex -
OL,13,Fit's essentially the use of drugs to
OL,14,Fenhance sex. The practice is more
OL,15,Fprevalent amongst gay, bi, and men who
OL,16,Fhave sex with men, but is not
OL,17,Fexclusive to this cohort.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/40
