OL,5,Clistening
OL,7,FOur investigation found that chemsex-
OL,8,Frelated drugs, which were once hidden
OL,9,Fbehind closed doors, are being used
OL,10,Fwith devastating consequences.
OL,12,FMore and more within the community are
OL,13,Fusing the potent and addictive drugs
OL,14,Frecreationally, likely by being in
OL,15,Fcloser proximity to the substances.
OL,16,FIt's a complicated link but hence why
OL,17,Fwe're using the term 'chemsex-related
OL,18,Fdrugs'.
OL,20,FWhat are chemsex-related drugs?
