OL,7,FThe two illegal drugs which
OL,8,Fprofessionals are most concerned about
OL,9,Fare GHB/GBL and Crystal Meth.
OL,11,FGHB/GBL is a Class B substance -
OL,12,Fcommonly referred to as 'G'. It's a
OL,13,Fcolourless liquid which can make the
OL,14,Fuser feel relaxed and aroused. But
OL,15,Fit's extremely easy to overdose on,
OL,16,Fjust a millilitre extra in a dose can
OL,17,Fbe fatal.
