OL,7,FCrystal Meth is a Class A substance -
OL,8,Foften referred to as 'Tina' - a
OL,9,Fmethamphetamine which can induce
OL,10,Feuphoria and arousal. But the harms
OL,11,Ffrom this particularly potent drug
OL,12,Finclude paranoia and psychosis,
OL,13,Fsomething healthcare professionals are
OL,14,Fextremely concerned by.
