OL,7,FHe died at that address, his body
OL,8,Fhaving lain undiscovered for 17 hours.
OL,10,FTahir had Crystal Meth, GHB and
OL,11,FKetamine in his system when he died.
OL,12,FHis dad found out that Tahir had been
OL,13,Fengaging with these types of drugs on
OL,14,Fand off since he was a teenager.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/40
