OL,7,FUnderstanding the full extent of the
OL,8,Fissue chemsex presents is difficult,
OL,9,Fas data is not readily available for
OL,10,Fthis type of drug usage.
OL,12,FDr Naomi Fitzgerald, a sexual health
OL,13,Fconsultant at King's College Hospital
OL,14,Fin London, has seen a rise in chemsex
OL,15,Fover the last decade, but says
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals and
OL,17,Fgovernment officials are largely in
OL,18,Fthe dark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/40
