OL,7,FITV News can reveal almost a third of
OL,8,Fall drug related presentations at
OL,9,FKing's College Hospital are from
OL,10,FGBL/GHB and Crystal Meth.
OL,12,FBut Dr Fitzgerald took it upon herself
OL,13,Fto pull out this data, it's not
OL,14,Fsomething easily available.
OL,16,FThe NHS uses codes for drugs like
OL,17,Falcohol and some Class A substances.
OL,18,FIt means they can track data and put
OL,19,Fmoney towards various issues. That's
OL,20,Fnot the case for the likes of G or
OL,21,FCrystal Meth.
