OL,7,FWithout a specific code healthcare
OL,8,Fprofessionals cannot quantify the
OL,9,Fscale of the issue, and therefore
OL,10,Ffunding cannot be allocated.
OL,12,FDr Fitzgerald added: "Without a
OL,13,Fspecific code for this issue, it is
OL,14,Fstill kind of going under the radar
OL,15,Fsomewhat and there isn't enough money
OL,16,Ffor us to deal with it effectively."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/40
