OL,7,F'You could refer to this as a kind of
OL,8,Fa silent crisis or epidemic...it's
OL,9,Fhappening, we know that it's
OL,10,Fhappening.'
OL,12,F'G' is particularly concerning for
OL,13,Fmany professionals in LGBT+ spaces
OL,14,Fbecause of it's potency, as just a few
OL,15,Fdrops can cause seizures and coma, and
