OL,7,FCapturing the data surrounding Crystal
OL,8,FMeth and GHB usage is also
OL,9,Fcomplicated. For example, ITV News has
OL,10,Fbeen told that testing for GHB/GBL
OL,11,Fwhen someone dies isn't routine,
OL,12,Fmeaning evidence of the harms
OL,13,Fsurrounding these substances could be
OL,14,Fgoing largely unnoticed.
OL,16,FMarc Svensson, a social psychologist
OL,17,Ffounded 'You are Loved' partly to
OL,18,Fevidence the high prevalence of
OL,19,Fsuicide and drug related deaths in the
OL,20,FLGBT+ community through data
OL,21,Fcollection.
