OL,7,FSvensson told ITV News: "It's complex
OL,8,Fto begin with, to test for GHB in a
OL,9,Fpost mortem exam... there are a number
OL,10,Fof barriers, cost being one, so
OL,11,Fresources being one, which the
OL,12,Fgovernment has been made aware of."
OL,14,FIn 2020, the previous government were
OL,15,Fmade aware of the harms specifically
OL,16,Frelating to 'G' within parts of the
OL,17,FLGBT+ community, and accepted
OL,18,Frecommendations to reduce the harms of
OL,19,Fthis substance, but only one of these
